The paper discusses variable ordering heuristics in constraint satisfaction problems (CSPs), which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of constraint weights and arc consistency, which are concepts commonly used in data structures (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL).
